LanguageData.ArachnaeBase_Race_Larva.label: Arachne larva species
LanguageData.ArachnaeBase_Race_Larva.description: One of the auxiliary insects of Arachne, it is the foundation of the Zerg race.
LanguageData.ArachnaeBase_Race_Scavenger.label: Arachne Scavenger
LanguageData.ArachnaeBase_Race_Scavenger.description: One of Arachne's parasitic worms, a creature of low intelligence that can perform the work of planting, harvesting, carrying, cleaning, and digging, and is destined to die after spending a short time.
